26
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:25,060
这是什么
What is this?

27
00:00:25,060 --> 00:00:27,340
是我记错了  还是我们没讨论过这事
Am I mistaken, or did we not have this discussion?

28
00:00:27,340 --> 00:00:28,730
别再打给我了
Don't call me again.

29
00:00:28,730 --> 00:00:30,650
你得告诉路易你一直在跟埃斯特上床
You need to tell Louis you've been sleeping with Esther.

30
00:00:30,650 --> 00:00:31,990
我们只睡了一次
We slept together one time.

31
00:00:31,990 --> 00:00:32,710
有什么区别呢
What difference does that make?

32
00:00:32,710 --> 00:00:34,330
你向他承诺了你不会这么做
You promised him you wouldn't do it at all.

33
00:00:34,330 --> 00:00:35,500
我得告诉你一件事
I need to tell you something.

34
00:00:35,500 --> 00:00:37,210
-你向我保证过的  -我告诉你
- You made a promise to me! - I'm telling you.

35
00:00:37,210 --> 00:00:39,500
因为他在可怜的童年时期遭受了什么破事
Because he's so messed up from whatever goddamn thing

36
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:41,000
导致他现在这么人渣...
happened to him in his pathetic childhood, he can't--

37
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:42,360
闭嘴
Shut the hell up!

38
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:07,420
给杰里・迈耶斯打个电话
Get me Jerry Myers on the phone.

39
00:01:07,420 --> 00:01:08,870
杰里・迈耶斯
Jerry Myers?

40
00:01:09,390 --> 00:01:10,490
路易  发生什么事了
Louis, what happened?

41
00:01:10,860 --> 00:01:11,780
我告诉你发生什么事了
I'll tell you what happened.

42
00:01:11,780 --> 00:01:13,020
哈维揍了我一拳
Harvey took a goddamn swing at me.

43
00:01:13,020 --> 00:01:15,010
-就是发生了这事儿  -天呐
- That's what happened. - Oh, my god.

44
00:01:15,010 --> 00:01:17,080
是啊  "天呐"  我要告死他
Yeah, "Oh, my god," I'm gonna sue the shit out of him.

45
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:18,150
好了  路易  你受伤了
Okay, Louis, you're hurt.

46
00:01:18,150 --> 00:01:19,500
你要做的第一件事是弄些冰块来
The first thing you need to do is get some ice

47
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:20,270
并且冷静下来
and calm down.

48
00:01:20,270 --> 00:01:21,810
你没听见我说的话吗
Did you not just hear me?

49
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:25,890
他打了我然后把我摔在了一张咖啡桌上
He hit me and then he threw me into a coffee table,

50
00:01:25,890 --> 00:01:28,160
所以我要告死他
so I am going to sue the shit out of him!

51
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:29,960
我不认为起诉哈维是解决之道
I don't think suing Harvey is the answer.

52
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:33,060
你当然不觉得了  因为你想要保护他
Of course you don't, because you want to protect him

53
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:34,800
就像当时你骗我
like you did when you lied to me

54
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:36,610
没把他对埃斯特做的事告诉我一样
about what he did to Esther.

55
00:01:36,610 --> 00:01:39,840
听我说  我告诉哈维要他自己和你坦白
Listen to me: I told Harvey to tell you himself.

56
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:40,850
而我骗了你
And I lied to you

57
00:01:40,850 --> 00:01:42,630
是因为我知道你要不是听他亲口说
because I knew something like this would happen

58
00:01:42,630 --> 00:01:44,600
就会发生像现在这样的事
if you didn't hear it directly from him.

59
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:46,940
确实是发生了  唐娜
Well, it did happen, Donna.

60
00:01:50,060 --> 00:01:52,380
现在马上给我打电话给杰里・迈耶斯
Now get me Jerry Myers on the phone.

61
00:01:52,660 --> 00:01:54,350
你想要我这么做  我会做的
You want me to do that, I will.

62
00:01:56,870 --> 00:01:59,140
但你总是说我们是一家人
But you've always said we're a family,

63
00:02:00,610 --> 00:02:04,560
而家丑不可外扬
and families keep things like this in the family.

64
00:02:12,780 --> 00:02:14,860
我不确定说"恭喜"是否妥当
I'm not sure if congratulations are in order,

65
00:02:14,870 --> 00:02:16,010
但既然我们没有别的选择
but since we have no other choice,

66
00:02:16,010 --> 00:02:18,470
