I'm going to choose congratulations.

67
00:02:18,470 --> 00:02:20,380
-你看见那个备忘了  -看见了
- You saw the memo? - I did.

68
00:02:20,380 --> 00:02:21,740
你要当合伙人了
You're making partner.

69
00:02:21,740 --> 00:02:23,280
不  瑞秋  我不会当的
No, Rachel, I'm not.

70
00:02:23,610 --> 00:02:24,730
什么意思
What do you mean?

71
00:02:24,770 --> 00:02:26,440
杰西卡要我拒绝
Jessica told me to turn it down.

72
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:29,390
