Said it would draw too much attention to me.

73
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:30,400
简直疯了
That's crazy.

74
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,320
假如你拒绝了  就会吸引更多的注意力
If you turn it down, you'll draw even more attention to yourself.

75
