我就是这么和她说的
That's exactly what I told her.

76
00:02:33,550 --> 00:02:34,550
那她怎么说
And what did she say?

77
00:02:34,550 --> 00:02:36,270
她说假如我足够聪明  不上法学院
She said that if I'm smart enough to be a lawyer

78
00:02:36,270 --> 00:02:37,880
也能成为律师  那我也就足够聪明
without going to law school, I should be smart enough

79
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:39,780
能想出个借口拒绝掉
to come up with an excuse to turn it down.

80
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:40,860
放屁
Oh, that's bullshit.

81
00:02:40,860 --> 00:02:42,550
你以为我不想当合伙人吗
You think I don't want this?

82
00:02:43,700 --> 00:02:44,720
我想的
I do.

83
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:48,210
当我们一直都知道我永远也当不了合伙人
But we've always known I was never gonna make partner.

84
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:51,680
好吧  那你准备怎么办
Okay. What are you gonna do?

85
00:02:51,740 --> 00:02:54,950
我要做和我惯常做法相反的事
I am gonna do the exact opposite of what I usually do.

86
00:02:54,950 --> 00:02:56,820
我不会去证明杰西卡错了
Instead of trying to prove Jessica wrong,

87
00:02:56,820 --> 00:02:58,510
而是会想出一个合理的借口
I'm gonna come up with a legitimate excuse

88
00:02:58,510 --> 00:02:59,890
解释我为何不能接受
for why I can't accept it.

89
00:03:03,940 --> 00:03:05,000
杰西卡
Jessica,

90
00:03:05,740 --> 00:03:07,410
我要知道你过来
if I knew you were coming over,

91
00:03:07,410 --> 00:03:09,390
会准备好龙舌兰和鸡蛋的
I would have made us some tequila and eggs.

92
00:03:09,390 --> 00:03:10,900
而我会用它们糊你一脸
And I would have thrown them in your face.

93
00:03:10,900 --> 00:03:12,240
那可不怎么友好啊
Well, that doesn't seem very nice.

94
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,860
我准备它们是想讨你欢心的
I cooked them just like you like them.

95
00:03:13,860 --> 00:03:15,200
你觉得这很有趣吗
You think this is funny?

96
00:03:15,510 --> 00:03:16,980
你攻击了一名冠名合伙人
You assaulted a name partner.

97
00:03:16,980 --> 00:03:18,740
而我在和你打哈哈就是因为我不想听这个
And I'm making jokes because I don't want to hear it,

98
00:03:18,740 --> 00:03:20,010
因为他是罪有应得
because he got what he deserved.

99
00:03:20,010 --> 00:03:21,960
我不在乎他有多大罪过
I don't care if he deserved a court martial.

100
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:24,770
那种行为不能存在于我的律所当中
That kind of behavior cannot exist in my firm!

101
00:03:25,050 --> 00:03:25,990
你是说我们的律所吧
You mean our firm?

102
00:03:25,990 --> 00:03:27,360
假如是我们的律所
If it's our firm,

103
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:29,240
那么也是路易的律所
then it's Louis's firm, too.

104
00:03:29,650 --> 00:03:31,980
好了  我明白你的意思了
Okay, you made your point.

105
00:03:31,980 --> 00:03:33,150
我不会再犯了
I won't do it again.

106
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:35,100
你以为我大老远跑到你这里来
You think I came all the way down here

107
00:03:35,100 --> 00:03:36,440
只为了说教你吗
just to give you a speech?

108
00:03:36,450 --> 00:03:38,990
你从明天开始休两周的假
You're taking two weeks starting tomorrow.

109
00:03:38,990 --> 00:03:40,190
我去度假
Me going on vacation

110
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:42,070
可不能阻止路易对付我
isn't gonna stop Louis from coming at me.

111
00:03:42,070 --> 00:03:43,870
会阻止的  因为假如在之后的两周内
Yes, it is, because if you set foot

112
00:03:43,870 --> 00:03:45,990
你踏进办公室附近的任何区域
anywhere near the office in the next two weeks,

113
00:03:45,990 --> 00:03:48,480
我保证他会申请停你职停三个月的
I guarantee he will call for a three-month suspension.

114
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:49,370
那就不要让他这么做啊
Then don't let him.

115
00:03:49,380 --> 00:03:51,090
哈维  我们律所是有规章制度的
Harvey, there are bylaws in place,

116
00:03:51,090 --> 00:03:54,160
而阻止他的唯一办法就是你休假
and the only way to stop him is you being on vacation.

117
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,550
唯一的问题是
The only problem with that is,

118
00:03:55,550 --> 00:03:57,720
人人都知道我从不休假
everyone knows I don't take vacations.

119
00:03:58,620 --> 00:04:01,880
那为何我手上有你两个月前
Then why am I holding your request

120
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:03,870
写的休假申请
that you filled out two months ago?

121
00:04:04,340 --> 00:04:05,900
路易不会买账的
Louis is never going to buy that.

122
00:04:05,900 --> 00:04:08,340
我才不管他是否买账呢
I don't give a shit whether he buys it or not.

123
00:04:08,770 --> 00:04:10,600
但在你开始你的小旅途之前
But before you go on your little trip,

124
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:13,400
你得夹着尾巴去找他
you're going to go to him with your tail between your legs

125
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:17,510
然后告诉他你之前百分百错了
and tell him that you were 100% wrong.

126
00:04:26,290 --> 00:04:27,860
杰西卡  你好呀
Jessica, hey.

127
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,200
有什么能为您效劳
What can I do for you?

128
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:29,970
你可以告诉我
Well, you can tell me

129
00:04:29,970 --> 00:04:32,990
为何提名迈克・罗斯做初级合伙人
why you nominated Mike Ross for junior partner

130
00:04:32,990 --> 00:04:34,630
但却没想着要知会我一声
and didn't think to run it by me.

131
00:04:34,710 --> 00:04:36,450
这是公开提名
It's an open nomination.

132
00:04:36,450 --> 00:04:38,010
我不觉得自己必须和你说
I didn't think I had to.

133
00:04:38,010 --> 00:04:39,390
我没说你必须
I didn't say you had to.

134
00:04:39,390 --> 00:04:41,350
我只是问你为什么没说
I asked you why you didn't.

135
00:04:41,350 --> 00:04:42,360
我不明白
I don't understand.

136
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,420
是你逼他和我合作的
You were the one who forced him to work with me.

137
00:04:44,420 --> 00:04:47,250
我是说和他合作  而不是背着我提名他
I said work with him, not nominate him behind my back

138
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:48,790
只为了对付哈维
just to stick it to Harvey.

139
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:52,710
杰西卡  我们还要讨论几次这件事
Jessica, how many times are we gonna have this conversation?

140
00:04:53,010 --> 00:04:54,710
你给了我一个求和的机会
You gave me a chance to make peace

141
00:04:54,710 --> 00:04:55,600
而我抓住了这个机会
and I took it.

142
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,210
而且到现在我也没听到一个好理由
And I still haven't heard one good reason

143
00:04:57,210 --> 00:04:58,960
解释为何不能给迈克升职
why Mike shouldn't be promoted.

144
00:04:59,100 --> 00:05:02,030
我没说他不够格当合伙人
Oh, I didn't say he didn't deserve to be partner.

145
00:05:03,450 --> 00:05:06,010
那我撤回我的备忘
Then how about I retract my memo

146
00:05:06,090 --> 00:05:08,060
让哈维来提名他如何
and let Harvey nominate him instead?

147
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:10,960
除非有原因导致这样你也不愿意
Unless there's some reason why you don't want that either.

148
00:05:10,970 --> 00:05:13,090
因为与其跟我谈这件事
Because instead of talking to me about this,

149
00:05:13,090 --> 00:05:16,060
你更该跟我谈谈昨晚路易和哈维之间
you should be talking to me about what happened last night

150
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:17,580
发生的事
between louis and harvey.

151
00:05:59,090 --> 00:06:01,650
-进展如何  -不太好
- How's it going? - Not great.

152
00:06:01,820 --> 00:06:04,040
你还没找到拒绝提名的方法
You haven't found a way to turn down the nomination?

153
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,950
我想出了15种拒绝的方法
Oh, I've found 15 ways to turn it down.

154
00:06:05,950 --> 00:06:07,230
但都不够好
But none of them are good enough.

155
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:10,220
肯定有一个很完美
Come on, one of them has to be good enough.

156
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:11,980
瑞秋  拒绝的理由不是重点
Rachel, it's not about the excuse,

157
00:06:11,980 --> 00:06:13,900
重点是我得能直视那些人的眼睛
it's about me being able to look these people in the eye

158
00:06:13,900 --> 00:06:15,270
说服他们相信这个理由
and convince them that it's true,

159
00:06:15,270 --> 00:06:16,610
可我做不到
and I can't do that.

160
00:06:16,780 --> 00:06:17,680
好吧
Okay.

161
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,770
那你要怎么办
What are you gonna do?

162
00:06:19,990 --> 00:06:21,050
不知道
I don't know.

163
00:06:21,340 --> 00:06:22,350
我知道
I do.

164
00:06:23,730 --> 00:06:24,970
你要处理这个
You're doing this.

165
00:06:26,110 --> 00:06:27,420
作为经营合伙人
As managing partner,

166
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:30,050
我正式委派给你第一个案子
I am officially giving you your first case.

167
00:06:30,050 --> 00:06:31,680
-天哪  -怎么了
- Oh my god. - What?

168
00:06:32,810 --> 00:06:35,510
经营合伙人给初级合伙人
It's tradition that the managing partner

169
00:06:35,510 --> 00:06:39,460
分配升职后第一个案子是律所的传统
to give all new junior partners their first case.

170
00:06:39,460 --> 00:06:41,490
-这是那个案子吗  -没错
- Is that what this is? - Yes, it is.

171
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,890
恭喜你  迈克
Congratulations, Mike.

172
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,950
虽然此事不在我计划之中
