173
00:06:44,950 --> 00:06:47,140
但我是真心认为你值得这个职位
but I really did mean it when I said you deserve it.

174
00:06:47,140 --> 00:06:48,490
谢谢你  杰西卡
Thank you, Jessica.

175
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:55,500
