Well, that means there's only one thing left to do.

179
00:07:05,590 --> 00:07:07,130
瑞秋・伊丽莎白・赞恩
Rachel Elizabeth Zane,

180
00:07:07,510 --> 00:07:08,710
你愿意做我成为合伙人后
will you be the associate

